<br>
Getting up to floor 5 by yourself can be tricky, but I have it down to a science.<br>
<br>
You ITU past the first 2 floors, floor 3 just run through really quick. Floor 4 I DA and run for it, once on 5 I camp out really quick then just kill the ring dude over and over.  You just need your key's, you need to know the route well, and you need a SoW.<br>
<br>
